OL,3,CCalls for Translink to compensate
OL,4,Cbusinesses hit by Boyne Bridge closure
OL,6,FTranslink should pay compensation to
OL,7,Fbusinesses affected by the closure of
OL,8,Fthe Boyne Bridge in Belfast, a member
OL,9,Fof the legislative assembly (MLA) has
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FWork at the site is being undertaken
OL,13,Fby Translink and started late last
OL,14,Fyear.
OL,16,FIt is part of plans to redevelop the
OL,17,Farea surrounding the city's new
OL,18,Ftransport hub, Grand Central Station.
