OL,3,CCalls for Translink to compensate
OL,4,Cbusinesses hit by Boyne Bridge closure
OL,6,FThe DUP's Edwin Poots, who represents
OL,7,Fthe area at Stormont, told UTV that
OL,8,Fthe estimated cost of removing the
OL,9,Fbridge is around #6million.
OL,11,FHe added that the closure of the
OL,12,Fbridge, added to associated traffic
OL,13,Fcongestion, has resulted in some
OL,14,Ftraders losing between 30-40% of
OL,15,Fincome.
OL,17,F"This is purely Translink's
OL,18,Fresponsibility," said the MLA.
