OL,3,CCalls for Translink to compensate
OL,4,Cbusinesses hit by Boyne Bridge closure
OL,6,F"They have started a process of work
OL,7,Fwithout having the proper planning in
OL,8,Fplace.
OL,10,F"The consequence of that has been that
OL,11,Fafter 3 months they have made a hole
OL,12,Fin the bridge and that is all, but
OL,13,Fthey have caused these people to lose
OL,14,Fconsiderable amounts of money and it
OL,15,Fis grossly unfair and up to Translink
OL,16,Fto identify what the actual loss is
OL,17,Fand compensate the traders for that."
