OL,4,Cbusinesses hit by Boyne Bridge closure
OL,6,FIn a statement, Translink told UTV:
OL,7,F"Planning permission was granted for
OL,8,FBelfast Grand Central Station by the
OL,9,FDepartment for Infrastructure in March
OL,10,F2019, which included the removal of
OL,11,FDurham Street/Boyne Bridge and
OL,12,Fconstruction of a new road layout and
OL,13,Fsurrounding public realm space.
OL,15,F"This is a complicated project with
OL,16,Fmany phases of construction, and there
OL,17,Fhas been extensive engagement
OL,18,Fthroughout the scheme with local
OL,19,Fcommunity and business groups, which
OL,20,Fis continuing.
