OL,6,F"The new public realm works will bring
OL,7,Fmany benefits now and for the future
OL,8,Fwith enhanced access to the station
OL,9,Ffor everyone".
OL,11,FUTV asked Translink if it was
OL,12,Fconsidering a financial compensation
OL,13,Fscheme for businesses in the area
OL,14,Fsurrounding the Boyne Bridge which
OL,15,Fhave suffered turnover issues since
OL,16,Fthe road closure.
OL,18,FTranslink did not reply.
