OL,3,CCalls for Translink to compensate
OL,4,Cbusinesses hit by Boyne Bridge closure
OL,6,FKim Harris runs a business on Sandy
OL,7,FRow and said "it has been a nightmare"
OL,8,Fsince the bridge closed.
OL,10,F"It's really impacting business," she
OL,11,Fexplained.
OL,13,F"The new transport hub is fabulous.
OL,14,FIt's so good to have it in the area
OL,15,Fand will really pull the area up.
OL,17,F"Obviously there is some regeneration
OL,18,Fto be done, but either the bridge is
OL,19,Ftaken away very quickly or it's
OL,20,Freopened - I don't mind as long as we
OL,21,Fget back to normal."
