OL,3,CCalls for Translink to compensate
OL,4,Cbusinesses hit by Boyne Bridge closure
OL,6,FAs for compensation, Ms Harris said it
OL,7,F"would be really helpful".
OL,9,F"If the bridge is going to be closed
OL,10,Ffor a very, very long time, plus the
OL,11,Fimpact of the recent budget, all the
OL,12,Fexpenses for employees are going up -
OL,13,Fwe just worry that we might not be
OL,14,Fthere when it reopens you know."
OL,16,FWhile it remains unclear whether
OL,17,Fbusinesses will receive any money,
OL,18,Fwhat is certain is that #4million will
OL,19,Fbe coming to the area from the
OL,20,FDepartment for Communities as part of
OL,21,Fwider transport hub plans.
